<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>664</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhōng guó dà yǒu xī wàng 迦南664</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng guó dà yǒu xī wàng, zhōng guó dà yǒu xī wàng.
 shén de pū rén nǎ nǐ yào gāng qiáng, nǐ yào gāng qiáng.
 yòng xìn xīn de yǎn jīng chuān yuè hēi yè, míng tiān chōng mǎn liàng guāng.
 yǒu nǐ pò qiè de dǎo gào, zhōng guó dà yǒu xī wàng.
 shèng líng de shuǐ liú qì shì bàng bó, qì shì bàng bó shì bù kě dǎng.
 xiàng dōng liú a liú xiàng zhōng guó, zhōng guó dà yǒu xī wàng.
 guò qù màn zhǎng de suì yuè duō yǒu fēng yǔ, míng tiān yào zǒu xiàng huī huáng.
 shí dài de gōng rén nǎ zhǔ zhèng zài kàn nǐ, zhōng guó dà yǒu xī wàng.</lyrics>
</song>